{"tid":2090466,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"俄國修憲公投點算四分三選票 77.6%贊成 普京有望掌權至2036年 有輿論指增強普京統治合法性","createTime":"2020-07-02T07:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T16:43:28.000Z","uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1412af48052356b04ef38e4af81b5dab660349e6","tid":2090466,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T07:37:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200702/O3DPFS5LFGGEC5GDWSRXI66SJU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200702%2FO3DPFS5LFGGEC5GDWSRXI66SJU%2F&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8HbrkFmDP3UEX6OAVSOiSMc%3D&h=255973c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200702%2FO3DPFS5LFGGEC5GDWSRXI66SJU%2F&h=aabe0155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200702/O3DPFS5LFGGEC5GDWSRXI66SJU/</a><br />\n俄羅斯將總統任期「歸零」的修憲公投結束，在點算超過四分三選票後，有超過77.6%選民支持修憲，讓總統普京可再參選兩次，掌權至2036年。<br />\n<br />\n公投自上周四開始，持續一個星期至香港時間今日凌晨結束，期間傳出不少選民受壓要投票及其他違規行為的報道。在周三最後一個投票日，俄羅斯政府便施以銀彈政策，鼓勵選民家庭投票。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯政府的大規模宣傳，加上反對派未能團結反擊，都有助普京得償所願，但公投以非正規手法來增加投票率及令人懷疑的投票法律基礎，都有損他的聲望。政治評論員分析普京在肺炎傳染風險高企的情況下仍堅持公投，反映他的潛在弱點，「普京内心缺乏信心及擔心未來，他希望確實地獲得公眾支持」。<br />\n<br />\n為了在舉行公投的同時應對武漢肺炎疫情，當局破天荒將公投時間拉長至一周，又將最後一天投票日列為假期，而且安排大抽獎送樓送車。<br />\n輿論認為目的是要提高投票率，盡量動員普京支持者投票，令到普京的永續大計顯得合法、正當。"},{"pid":"5ef88a4e6e5426aa8f8c6dcc67a1a5633a95c71e","tid":2090466,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T07:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3KfmK5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3KfmK5D.jpg&h=2b495cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6CBAPxg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6CBAPxg.png&h=98afefc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OZKnuxh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOZKnuxh.png&h=179d9449&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f289caf8a73c06291107ae46a7e31b2838c68dc","tid":2090466,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T07:53:25.000Z","msg":"沒有沒有沒有通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24832dac6f721613e1a1f3b126a53926f895e4d1","tid":2090466,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:12:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8492911cf0b752c98e71766aeb1c0fcfbba3d0","tid":2090466,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T09:42:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ef80bd6a1f4e21df04069eaf00481e1f9a5c47","tid":2090466,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T09:44:32.000Z","msg":"好過強國<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全票支持雜種永續"},{"pid":"2624313cb2f77f9eeee34a10f39baf9f7be46440","tid":2090466,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T09:46:23.000Z","msg":"As long as 普京存心撚鳩支那<br />\n我都支持到2036<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7358a11c9b501ef7b93bcbe128928f0f7564d3d4","tid":2090466,"uid":2889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T09:47:15.000Z","msg":"永續總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢算得民心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4af958d5b5921db66c20c91c96d89abdfb96894","tid":2090466,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T09:48:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1482ab128aab40ff27179ca4e21d1fcbed99dc","tid":2090466,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T10:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb26ea436e